###ICS:TASK_PAYLOAD###
Using only the retrieved chunks identified in SESSION_STATE, explain why webhook delivery may
fail with HTTP 422 on the target endpoint and what corrective steps are available.

Do not suggest re-registering the endpoint; the user has confirmed this was already attempted
and did not resolve the issue.
###END:TASK_PAYLOAD###

###ICS:OUTPUT_CONTRACT###
format:     JSON
schema: {
  "answer": "string",
  "citations": [
    {
      "doc_path":        "string",
      "section_heading": "string",
      "version_tag":     "string"
    }
  ],
  "version_mismatch": "boolean",
  "insufficient_context": "boolean"
}
variance:   "citations" MAY be an empty array only if "insufficient_context" is true;
            "version_mismatch" MUST be present even if false;
            "insufficient_context" MUST be present even if false
on_failure: Return { "status": "error", "reason": "<single-sentence description>" }
###END:OUTPUT_CONTRACT###
